she still stood up...!!\n< Serena >

No matter how defiled... how wounded, she never
gave up against a formidable enemy, did she?!!!\n< Serena >

Are you going to falter now, Serena...? Serena
Fuoco R. Brillante di Grazia!\n< Serena >

Right before me... within reach, my radiance is
seeking help...!!\n< Serena >

...What I need is not power, not the power to
oppress others...!\n< Serena >

It's the heart of compassion that thinks of others
and reaches out a hand...\n< Serena >

And... a strong, unbreakable heart like Lady
Erika's!!\n< Serena >

That's right. As long as the beating in my
chest... the sound does not cease... I must stand
up!\n< Serena >

With my heartbeat... with my feelings as my
sustenance...!!\n< Serena >
Clothe my body and become my shield... Affabile!\n< Serena >

To destroy the wicked ones who dare to tarnish my
shine!!\n< Serena >
Come now... you demonic spawn unlike any human...\n< Serena >

Let us see whether my spirit will be devoured or
your body will rot away...\n< Serena >
Let's settle this battle of the sexes!!\n< Serena >
神に祈る
